- [ ] `appmod_get_iac_rules` - Get Bicep best practices
- [ ] `get_errors` - Validate Bicep files
- [ ] `appmod_get_app_logs` - Retrieve application logs post-deployment
- [ ] `create_file` - Generate infrastructure files
